wrn_PendingChangesAdWordsCampaignsIgnore.en: Pending changes in your AdWords campaigns will be ignored.

wrn_NoSyncingAdWordsExecutedPriorToActiv.en: No syncing with AdWords will be executed prior to activating the clone process.

wrn_NotAllEntitiesClonedSomeTypesExtensi.en: Not all entities are cloned, such as (but not limited to) some types of extensions and targets.

wrn_StatusClonedCampaignsDefaultPaused.en: Status of cloned campaigns will default to Paused.
